: {}, "pageNumber": 0, "neatVersion": "4.4b", "version": "2026-03-30-base", "language": "en", "result_message": "Our detector is moderately confident that the text is written entirely by a human.", "result_sub_message": null, "document_classification": "HUMAN_ONLY", "inputText": "Most people quit their fitness goals within the first month. It’s not because they don’t care — it’s because motivation fades. I want to build a fitness accountability app designed specifically for busy professionals who struggle to stay consistent.

